{
  "texts": [
    "The coarse-grained macrofunction of computation enables computational systems to perform micro-functions according to specific usages and purposes.",
    "Considering ChatGPT as a cognitive artifact, at the highest level of analysis it performs the macro-function of information 8 Although this tool can also be used as an affective and emotional artifact by contributing to regulating and influencing the affective states of the user (Piredda 2020), in this paper I will characterize it only as a cognitive artifact that supports cognitive tasks.",
    "9 A task is \"any activity in which a person engages, given an appropriate setting, in order to achieve a specifiable class of objectives, final results, or terminal states of affairs\" (Carroll 1993, p. 8).",
    "Carroll defined a cognitive task as \"any task in which correct or appropriate processing of mental information is critical to successful performance\" (Carroll 1993, p. 10).",
    "processing by virtue of computations."
  ]
}